<h1>Workshops</h1>
<p><img src="./img/workshop.gif" hspace=10  vspace=5 align="right">Workshops at Techfest have been hands-on experiences, where there is a great deal of interaction between the participants and the speaker. The emphasis in the workshops is to provide good exposure about the latest developments in the field of science and technology to the participants as well as to be able to apply the theories and basics learnt into a working model.</p>
<p>A number of topics like User Centric Designs, Animation, Security, Robotics, Forensics, Smart Materials and Cryptography have been covered under workshops in previous editions of Techfest.</p>
<p>Every Techfest has left behind poignant memories for the organizers as well as the participants. It has also served as an inspiration to make the next edition more memorable. The Techfest team believes in change as its mantra for raising the standards of the fest & change it is that will be most prominently seen in Techfest 2006. </p>
